Package org.action.registration

Class RegistrationManager

java.lang.Object
org.action.registration.RegistrationManager
public class RegistrationManager extends Object
This class provides functionality for creating, storing, retrieving, and processing registrations. It handles user registration for projects, registration approval/rejection by managers, and officer assignment to projects.

    • processRegistration

      public void processRegistration(user usr, String registrationID, String action, ProjectManager proMan)
      Processes a registration by approving or rejecting it. Only HDBManager users can process registrations.
      Parameters:
      usr - The user processing the registration
      registrationID - The ID of the registration to process
      action - The action to take ("APPROVED" or "REJECTED")
      proMan - The ProjectManager instance to use for assigning officers
